summary: A small Nordic cottage near Riverwood
descriptionHtml:
ISSUES

I have been informed that I have accidentally edited Whiterun Breezehome, Abandoned Shack, Whiterun Stables, Whiterun Guard House, Whiterun Jorrvaskr, Whiterun Bannered Mare, and Vlindrel
Hall, I am not sure how to fix this or what it has done to these locations

the only known conflict so far is Breezehome fully upgraded so if you use that mod be aware I will try to fix it

If anyone else finds a conflict in the above locations please let me know, if the conflicts are game breaking I will remove the mod immediately

SOLUTION: load all breezehome mods last then should not not conflict, cheers [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/13794095][u][color=#0066cc]awjnash[/color][/u][/url] for finding a solution

Cheers

MOD

small lore friendly Nordic cottage with all crafting stations

There are a few little secrets inside so be sure to check everything

Most containers are named and designed in an attempt to offer unique storage

The key is inside the waterfall on the other side of the Riverwood bridge, Its easy to obtain at an early lvl

the cottage is on the path heading up to Bleak Falls Barrow

If you find an issue please feel free to comment and I will try to fix it

Hope you enjoy
author: Indarius
